## Bridge public_address (CORRECTED)

The earlier package incorrectly set `appservice.public_address` to the Synapse
URL. Per review, that field is for external public-media serving of the bridge
appservice and must stay unset while `public_media.enabled` is false. The value
was reverted to `null` on all three bridges. No bridge config change is part of
this package. `homeserver.address` (internal Synapse URL) was already correct
and is unchanged.
